  - kind:     json | toml | yaml | changelog | regex
  - field:    dot-path (json/toml/yaml only) — e.g. version, project.version,
              plugins[0].version
  - pattern:  regex with named (?<version>...) group (regex only)
  - replace:  template using {version} placeholder (regex only)
  - optional: bool (default false) — missing path is `n/a`, not error

Full schema + per-kind worked examples: docs/ship-milestone-reference.md.
